HEADWORD: Decreet
<hw>De*creet"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Decree</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>The final judgment
of the Court of Session, or of an inferior court, by which the question
at issue is decided.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

